@startuml
' Tech Challenge Fase 03 - Flow detalhado entre Serviços e Bancos de Dados
title Tech Challenge Fase 03 - Flow detalhado entre Serviços e Bancos de Dados

actor Cliente
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "Service Registry (Eureka)" as EUREKA
participant "Auth Service" as AUTH
participant "Keycloak" as KC
participant "Orchestrator Service" as ORQ
participant "Order Service" as ORDER
participant "Restaurant Service" as REST
participant "Payment Service" as PAY
participant "ProcPag" as PROCPAG
participant "RabbitMQ" as BROKER
participant "Payment Worker (Reprocessamento)" as WORKER

database "Auth DB (Postgres)" as AUTHDB
participant "Redis" as REDIS

database "Keycloak DB" as KCDB

database "Order DB (Postgres)" as ORDERDB

database "Restaurant DB (Postgres)" as RESTDB

database "Payment DB (Postgres)" as PAYDB

' Autenticação
Cliente -> APIGW: POST /auth/login
APIGW -> EUREKA: resolve auth-service
APIGW -> AUTH: encaminha login
AUTH -> AUTHDB: consulta/atualiza contexto local
AUTH -> KC: autentica usuário
KC -> KCDB: consulta realm/usuário
KCDB --> KC: dados de autenticação
KC --> AUTH: JWT / erro
AUTH --> APIGW: resposta de autenticação
APIGW --> Cliente: token JWT

' Logout
Cliente -> APIGW: POST /auth/logout (Bearer JWT)
APIGW -> REDIS: verifica blacklist
APIGW -> AUTH: encaminha logout
AUTH -> KC: revoga sessão
AUTH -> REDIS: blacklist:<jti> com TTL
AUTH --> APIGW: 204 No Content
APIGW --> Cliente: 204 No Content

' Pedido e Pagamento
Cliente -> APIGW: POST /orchestrator/requests (Bearer JWT)
APIGW -> ORQ: inicia orquestração
ORQ -> REST: valida restaurante/itens
REST -> RESTDB: consulta restaurante/itens
REST --> ORQ: validação OK
ORQ -> ORDER: cria pedido
ORDER -> ORDERDB: persiste pedido inicial
ORDER -> BROKER: publica pedido.criado
PAY -> BROKER: consome pedido.criado
PAY -> PAYDB: cria transação local
PAY -> PROCPAG: tenta pagamento externo
PROCPAG --> PAY: resultado pagamento
PAY -> PAYDB: atualiza status transação
PAY -> BROKER: publica pagamento.aprovado/pagamento.pendente
ORDER -> BROKER: consome eventos de pagamento
ORDER -> ORDERDB: atualiza status pedido
ORDER --> APIGW: status final
APIGW --> Cliente: resposta final

' Reprocessamento
WORKER -> BROKER: consome pagamento.pendente
WORKER -> PROCPAG: reprocessa pagamento
PROCPAG --> WORKER: resultado reprocessamento
WORKER -> BROKER: publica pagamento.aprovado
ORDER -> BROKER: consome pagamento.aprovado
ORDER -> ORDERDB: pedido = PAGO

@enduml
